com.github.kennedyoliveira.pastebin4j

Class UserInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kennedyoliveira.pastebin4j.UserInformation

  • public class UserInformation
extends java.lang.Object

    User information fetched from the API.

    This class is imutable, and only represents the information fetched.

    Currently the pastebin api doens't support altering this information, that why this class is immutable

    Since:
    1.0.0
